Bootstrap: docker
From: quay.io/biocontainers/nonpareil:3.5.5--r44h077b44d_2

%labels
Maintainer lowry-nitrogen-team
Description Singularity container for Nonpareil from quay.io/biocontainers/nonpareil

%help
This container wraps the BioContainers Nonpareil image.

Examples:
  singularity exec containers/nonpareil.sif nonpareil -h
  singularity shell containers/nonpareil.sif

%runscript
exec "$@"
